data.description: Priced to sell!!! Now's your chance to get a home in Deer Trail, a unique collection of neighborhoods at Bedico Creek Preserve. Deer Trail prides itself on being a conservation community that strives to conserve and preserve, all while living a private and peaceful lifestyle within a gated community. Some features of Deer Trail are miles of trails with beautiful wilderness views, natural wildlife habitats along our hundreds of acres of lakes, parks and nature preserves, and a comforting horse fence backdrop lining the property. The Barberry plan has 2175 square ft of living area that includes high ceilings in the open concept living and dining area. The Kitchen/Breakfast Nook off of the living area are tucked into the back of the home with views of the backyard. There are 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, all of which connect to the living space. The master bedroom includes a tray ceiling and an attached master bath that includes a walk-in closet, walk-in shower, jetted tub, and double vanities. This is a single-story home. Association dues are $1050 annually.
